<%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=EUC-KR"
    pageEncoding="EUC-KR"%>
<%@ taglib prefix="fmt" uri="http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/fmt" %>
<%-- /WebContent/jstl/jstlfmtEx2.jsp --%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="EUC-KR">
<title>형식 관련 태그 예제2</title>
</head>
<body>
<h3>Format 된 숫자를 일반 숫자로 변경</h3>
<fmt:parseNumber value="20,000" var="num1" pattern="##,###" />
<fmt:parseNumber value="10,000" var="num2" pattern="##,###" />
합: ${num1 + num2}<br>
합: <fmt:formatNumber value="${num1 + num2}" pattern="##,###" /><br>
합: <fmt:formatNumber value="${num1 + num2}" pattern="##,###" var="num3" />${num3}<br>
합: ${num3}

<h3>Format 된 날짜를 일반 날짜로 변경</h3>
<fmt:parseDate value="2020-05-08 12:00:00" pattern="yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss" var="day" />
날짜: ${day}<br>
<h3>문제: 2020-05-09의 요일을 출력하기</h3>
<fmt:parseDate value="2020-05-09" pattern="yyyy-MM-dd" var="tom" />
<fmt:formatDate value="${tom}" pattern="yyyy-MM-dd E요일" />
</body>
</html>